# The image build only needs the Dockerfile, scripts/, sample-input/, and the
# two release tarballs the workflow stages into the context. Exclude everything
# else (esp. the huge target/ and deps/ trees).
*
!Dockerfile
!scripts/
!sample-input/
!snip36-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
!snip36-deps-linux-x86_64.tar.gz
